Former Champ Sharapova Defeats Zakopalova in Wimbledon Third-Round Match

-- B y   C h r i s   E l s e r
-- 
2011-06-25T12:33:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-25/former-champ-sharapova-defeats-zakopalova-in-wimbledon-third-round-match.html
Former champion  Maria Sharapova 
defeated Klara Zakoplova of the  Czech Republic  in their third-
round match at Wimbledon.  Sharapova won 6-2, 6-3 to reach the fourth round for the
seventh time in 9 appearances at the All England Club. The 24-
year-old Russian won the Wimbledon title in 2004. The 29-year-
old Zakopalova was in the third round of a major for just the
third time in 32 appearances.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  